    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――そろそろ夏休みが終わる頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――そろそろ夏休みが終わる頃",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4656927109,
      "endTime": 57.892360687200004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ゆゆしき事態です\nいえ、これは非常事態と言わざるを得ません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ゆゆしき事態です\nいえ、これは非常事態と言わざるを得ません",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7990288417,
      "endTime": 66.1407067935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "確かに私達はBIG4になり日々忙しいです\n夏休みに入ってからも、ありがたいことに仕事続き",
      "translations": {
        "en": "確かに私達はBIG4になり日々忙しいです\n夏休みに入ってからも、ありがたいことに仕事続き",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3365340869,
      "endTime": 75.84249817530001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "時間を捻出するのにも苦労します\nだからと言って――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "時間を捻出するのにも苦労します\nだからと言って――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.0383254687,
      "endTime": 81.7284334103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "なんでまだ誰も、夏休みの宿題が終わってないんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "なんでまだ誰も、夏休みの宿題が終わってないんですか",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.89170386,
      "endTime": 86.64249760310001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "それは……仕事の反省会をしたり\nライブの見直しをするのに時間使いたくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "それは……仕事の反省会をしたり\nライブの見直しをするのに時間使いたくて……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.8383248965,
      "endTime": 94.8614312808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんと宿題しようと思って誘うんだけど\nつい一緒に反省会しちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "琴乃ちゃんと宿題しようと思って誘うんだけど\nつい一緒に反省会しちゃって……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.0572585742,
      "endTime": 102.0821564357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "な、夏休みの宿題は、最終週に全て倒すべし！\n……が成宮家の家訓ですの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "な、夏休みの宿題は、最終週に全て倒すべし！\n……が成宮家の家訓ですの",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2779837291,
      "endTime": 111.1946066539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "ノート開くと眠くなっちゃうんだよね～\n沙季ちゃんは進んでるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ノート開くと眠くなっちゃうんだよね～\n沙季ちゃんは進んでるの？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3904339473,
      "endTime": 117.6397308986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "はい、もちろん終わらせていますよ\n七月中に、全部、余すところなく、完璧に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "はい、もちろん終わらせていますよ\n七月中に、全部、余すところなく、完璧に",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.8237672806,
      "endTime": 128.5828603745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "一同",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おお～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "おお～！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.7786876679,
      "endTime": 131.1666704178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "もう、感心してる場合じゃありませんよ！\n夏休みの宿題は、勉強するだけが目的じゃありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "もう、感心してる場合じゃありませんよ！\n夏休みの宿題は、勉強するだけが目的じゃありません",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3425128937,
      "endTime": 139.8000037511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "長期休暇の中で、与えられた課題を、自分で組んだ\nスケジュールに沿って期日までに終わらせる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "長期休暇の中で、与えられた課題を、自分で組んだ\nスケジュールに沿って期日までに終わらせる……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.9678071976,
      "endTime": 147.5000017166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "そういう、社会人として……アイドルという仕事を\nする上で必要な精神を学ぶことも重要なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そういう、社会人として……アイドルという仕事を\nする上で必要な精神を学ぶことも重要なんです",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.6844215393,
      "endTime": 155.5475962639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "ましてや私達は今やBIG4の一角\nその自覚をしっかりもって活動しなくては……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ましてや私達は今やBIG4の一角\nその自覚をしっかりもって活動しなくては……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.7434235573,
      "endTime": 163.17843475339998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "けど、仕事やレッスンは自分達のペースで\nしっかりこなせているじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "けど、仕事やレッスンは自分達のペースで\nしっかりこなせているじゃない",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.3742620468,
      "endTime": 168.6000037511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわ。沙季の言う精神はすでに学んでいる\nでしたら、何も問題ないのでは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そうですわ。沙季の言う精神はすでに学んでいる\nでしたら、何も問題ないのでは？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.8017447472,
      "endTime": 176.98502264020001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
